Package: dosh
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Run a user shell in a container with working directory bind mounted.
 dosh(1) is an sh-compatible front-end for docker that runs commands in a new
 container; using the current user, with working directory bind mounted.

Package: dosh-docker-shell
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dosh
Description: Docker CLI plugin for dosh.
 Run a user shell in a container with working directory bind mounted.
 dosh(1) is an sh-compatible front-end for docker that runs commands in a new
 container; using the current user, with working directory bind mounted.

